{"tid":1658753,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"1020和理非","createTime":"2019-10-16T15:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T16:01:50.000Z","uid":313716,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"20da6d1768ab59f9e86d6bd0f028c6003c2ee0ad","tid":1658753,"uid":313716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:06:23.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過<br />\n佢遲唔打 早唔打 偏偏這個時候先來打<br />\n這個時候係民陣等緊不反對通知書<br />\nD狗見連登無聲氣話要裝修 就要死死地氣出不反<br />\n但佢地又唔想出不反 所以專登搵人打子杰<br />\n激起民怨，再起連登帶風氣話要裝修<br />\nD狗就大條道理出反對通知書<br />\n令和理非回合變反勇武<br />\n破壞我哋的成功方程式<br />\n大家諗下上一次和理飛回合已經係818<br />\n兩個月來都冇和理非遊行<br />\n1020係時候了<br />\n重現200萬人<br />\n<br />\n此外 請留意一下有D巴絲一聽到人話要1020主張和理非 no gear就話人哋on9<br />\n我哋運動一直秉持不分化 不指責 所以這班人有機會係班狗 出嚟帶風向<br />\n絕對不是自己人<br />\n1020和理非<br />\n1020和理非<br />\n1020和理非<br />\n重要嘅嘢講三次"},{"pid":"3d5f270702d55680ee6749b09cf9bd7c3463cc82","tid":1658753,"uid":313716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:07:03.000Z","msg":"1014民主法案集氣大會冇事"},{"pid":"96c933ba74a175e89b81e01e88d6404c3ea26782","tid":1658753,"uid":313716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:07:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dabd414cb86a710daaa929938e57fcceff16e1a1","tid":1658753,"uid":154257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:09:13.000Z","msg":"10月13日荃灣被捕義士post要幫手推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/enFqgS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/enFqgS</a>"},{"pid":"0f9887dee36bd3c96beccd9ef94eba3bea53b393","tid":1658753,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:12:54.000Z","msg":"【再次有圖有真相】令街坊知道1020遊行嘅最佳方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1657842\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1657842</a>"},{"pid":"cbabcebcf7441a1e3d1941429291c2522fa82104","tid":1658753,"uid":170143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:20:45.000Z","msg":